Prebon kissed Spears again, and than walked out of the base with her.

"You are welcome, and you may yet get a chance to thank me. We have 
to make this look real, so you are going to have to fly in on 
Ignatiu's back. Is that a problem?"

A shock came over Prebon. He had never before cared if any of his 
subjects didn't like what he was saying. It was an order, and they 
would obey. Maybe he was caring about her after all.
